    "longBusinessSummary": "Dabaco Group Joint Stock Company produces and sells animal feed in Vietnam. The company offers feed for pigs, chicken, and aqua under the Dabaco, Topfeeds, Kinh Bac, Khangti Vina, Nasaco, and Growfeeds names. The company is also involved in the pig and chicken breeding activities; produces and sells chicken eggs and vegetable oils under DABACO brand; operation of pig and chicken contracted farms; production and trading of cattle, poultry, waterfowl and aquatic breeds; packaging services; provision of chicken meat; and production of food, such as pork, chicken, eggs, sausages, hams, and canned food. In addition, it invests in industrial zones, urban zone facilities, and infrastructure and real estate properties. Further, it engages in the accommodation of restaurants, dining, and commerce services; production of fats, organic microbial fertilizers, drugs, pharmaceutical chemicals, and medicinal materials; construction of railways, houses, and road and civil works. The company was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Bac Ninh, Vietnam.",
